'''''Mr. Bliss''''' (Мистер Блисс) is a [[2004]] Russian-language adaptation of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]'s story [[Mr. Bliss|of the same name]], produced by "Tolkien Texts Translation". The animated cartoon is 33 minutes in length, and narrated by Dmitri Matveyev. The film's animation style is heavily based on Tolkien's own original drawings of ''Mr. Bliss'' that have appeared in various editions of the story. The film was shown at [[Tolkien Thing]] 2006 and [[Ring*Con 2006]].

